        "start": 202.19,
        "end": 211.471
      },
      {
        "segment": "Firstly, there was an awareness of the efficiency for experience of mind, body, and spirit.",
        "start_offset": 841,
        "end_offset": 932,
        "start": 215.051,
        "end": 244.712
      },
      {
        "segment": "Secondly, there was an awareness of the most efficacious nature or, if you will, significator of mind, body, and spirit.",
        "start_offset": 933,
        "end_offset": 1053,
        "start": 247.573,
        "end": 282.514
      },
      {
